data.description: Absolutely beautiful totally updated 2 houses in one price. Must see to appreciate. Main house has over 3628 sq ft on 1.8 acres. 4 or 5 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths, 3 living areas. Large main living area with walls of windows overlooking exercise room & beautiful yard, patio & above ground pool. Large dining can seat 10-12. Amazing updated kitchen includes newer cabinets, pantry, built-in double oven, gas stove, granite countertops, tile backsplashes, stainless steel appliances. Huge primary bedroom downstairs. Totally updated bath, large tiled shower, private patio off main bedroom. Large study, den/media room w/gas log fireplace, built-in screen and sound system. Huge room size utility room w/extra cabinets & counter space and room for 2nd refrigerator. Large  bedroom & 2 baths down, 2 bedrooms & bath upstairs. Totally updated over 950 sq ft 2nd house is just as nice as main house, 2 BR or 2 living, LVP floor coverings, granite countertops, SS appliances. Call 580-248-8800 for showing or text 580-581-7870 for more details.
